            <p>Our website is an initiative to redistribute unsold and excess food in restaurants to our needy people in NGOs so that there is reduced levels of wasting of food in our society. A shoutout to all restaurants to sign up for this so that you can distribute your food surplus to the needy and get yur CSR points right :)! and to all the NGOs so that you can collect food from the restaurants of your choice.</p>
      <div class="text" style="font-size:20px;background-color: #eff6ef; /* dark green */;padding: 20px;border-radius: 10%;font-weight: bold;"><b>
